title: Patriots-Jets, NBA season, AFC, and the Herd Hierarchy
itunes:title: Patriots-Jets, NBA season, AFC, and the Herd Hierarchy
description:
Colin talks about the Patriots destroying the Jets on Monday Night Football, the gap between New England and the rest of the NFL, the mistakes the Jets continue to make, why the AFC race is already over, why the NBA needs a good villain, and the new Herd Hierarchy. Guests include Greg Jennings, Peter King, Rob Parker, and Chris Haynes.
